
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Yes' radio button from Contrast enhanced of Page 03
And	I go to Page 04 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Mass' from the dropdown menu
Then 'I describe' box is enabled and automatically selected
And 'I know' box is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and automatically selected
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' tab is enabled

When I am on 'Characterization II' tab
Then 'No displacement' radio button is enabled
And 'Ongoing continuation of the orthotopic thyroid gland' radio button is enabled
And 'Right side close to carina' radio button is enabled
And 'Dumbbell-shaped' radio button is enabled
And 'Infiltration' radio button is enabled

And 'Scalopping/diluted pedicle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Widened neuroforamen' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pressure erosion rib' checkbox is enabled
And 'Locoregional osteolysis' checkbox is enabled

And 'None' radio button is enabled
And 'Low' radio button is enabled
And 'Strong' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Infiltration' radio button
Then 'Pleura' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pericardium' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bones' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Low' radio button
Then 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Strong' radio button
Then 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled
